HEADWORD: Growse
<hw>Growse</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <ety>[Cf.
<ets>gruesome</ets>, <ets>grewsome</ets>, and G. <ets>grausen</ets> to
make shudder, shiver.]</ety> <def>To shiver; to have chills.</def>
